						<summary>

						<p>The inscription is damaged. It consists of a few verses eulogising the exploits of the chiefs Vāṇarpirāṉ Rājarājaṉ, his son Ponparappina-perumāḷ; and also of his descendants (?) Añjādaperumāḷ and a chief (name not clear) who gets the epithet “Vaḍugeṟinda” </p>						

